file.content:
# OpenAPI version identifier - required for OpenAPI 3.0 domains
openapi: 3.0.0

#######################
# Optional info section
#######################
info:
  title: INGV Earthworm Definitions
  description: |
    INGV Earthworm definitions!
  version: 1.2.0

components:
  ####################
  # Common data models
  ####################
  schemas:
    ewLogo__type:
      type: string
      description: Type description | ???
    ewLogo__module:
      type: string
      description: Module description | ???
    ewLogo__installation:
      type: string
      description: Installation description | ???
      example: INST_INGV
    ewLogo__user:
      type: string
      description: User | ???
      example: ew
    ewLogo__hostname:
      type: string
      description: Hostname | ???
      example: hew3.int.ingv.it
    ewLogo__instance:
      type: string
      description: Instance description | ???
      example: hew3_mole
    qAuthor:
      type: string
      description: qAuthor description
      example: 014101073:028130073
    quake2kSchema:
      properties:
        ewMessage:
          required:
            - quakeId
            - version
            - originTime
            - latitude
            - longitude
            - depth
          properties:
            quakeId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id_localspace'
            originTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__ot'
            latitude:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/latitude'
            longitude:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/longitude'
            depth:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/depth'
            rms:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__rms'
            dmin:
              type: number
              description: dmin description | ???
              format: double
            ravg:
              type: number
              description: ravg description | ???
              format: double
            gap:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/azimutal_gap'
            nph:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__nph'
        ewLogo:
          required:
            - type
            - module
            - installation
            - instance
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              description: Type description | ???
              example: TYPE_QUAKE2K
            module:
              type: string
              description: Module description | ???
              example: MOD_BINDER_EW
            installation:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__installation'
            user:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__user'
            hostname:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__hostname'
            instance:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__instance'

    hyp2000arcSchema:
      properties:
        ewMessage:
          required:
            - quakeId
            - version
            - originTime
            - latitude
            - longitude
            - depth
          properties:
            quakeId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id_localspace'
            version:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/type_origin__version_name'
            originId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id'
            originTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__ot'
            latitude:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/latitude'
            longitude:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/longitude'
            depth:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/depth'
            nph:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__nph'
            nphS:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__nph_s'
            nphtot:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__nph_tot'
            nPfm:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__nph_fm'
            gap:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/azimutal_gap'
            dmin:
              type: number
              description: dmin description | ???
              format: double
            rms:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__rms'
            e0az:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e0_az'
            e0dp:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e0_dip'
            e0:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e0'
            e1az:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e1_az'
            e1dp:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e1_dip'
            e1:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e1'
            e2:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__e2'
            erh:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__err_h'
            erz:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__err_z'
            Md:
              type: number
              description: Md description | ???
              format: double
            reg:
              type: string
              description: ingvQuality description | ???
              example: ' '
            labelpref:
              type: string
              description: ingvQuality description | ???
              example: ' '
            Mpref:
              type: number
              description: Mpref description | ???
              format: double
            wtpref:
              type: number
              description: wtpref description | ???
              format: double
            mdtype:
              type: string
              description: ingvQuality description | ???
              example: D
            mdmad:
              type: number
              description: mdmad description | ???
              format: double
            mdwt:
              type: number
              description: mdwt description | ???
              format: double
            ingvQuality:
              type: string
              description: ingvQuality description | ???
              example: DD
            amplitudeMagnitude:
              type: number
              description: amplitudeMagnitude description | col37 F3.2
              format: double
            numberOfAmpMagWeightCode:
              type: number
              description: numberOfAmpMagWeightCode description | col97 F4.1
              format: double
            medianAbsDiffAmpMag:
              type: number
              description: medianAbsDiffAmpMag description | col105 F3.2
              format: double
            preferredMagLabel:
              type: string
              description: preferredMagLabel description | ???
            preferredMag:
              type: number
              description: preferredMag description | ???
              format: double
            numberOfPreferredMags:
              type: number
              description: numberOfPreferredMags description | ???
              format: double
            phases:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/hyp2000arc__phases'
        ewLogo:
          required:
            - type
            - module
            - installation
            - instance
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              description: Type description | ???
              example: TYPE_HYP2000ARC
            module:
              type: string
              description: Module description | ???
              example: MOD_EQASSEMBLE
            installation:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__installation'
            user:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__user'
            hostname:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__hostname'
            instance:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__instance'
  
    hyp2000arc__phases:
      type: array
      items:
        required:
          - net
          - sta
          - comp
          - loc
        properties:
          net:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/net'
          sta:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/sta'
          comp:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/cha'
          loc:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/loc'
          latitude:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/latitude'
          longitude:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/longitude'
          Plabel:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: ' '
          Slabel:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: ' '
          Ponset:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: P
          Sonset:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: ' '
          Pat:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__ot'
          Sat:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/origin__ot'
          Pres:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Sres:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Pqual:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Squal:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          codalen:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          codawt:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Pfm:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: ' '
          Sfm:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: ' '
          datasrc:
            type: string
            description: Todo description | ???
            example: W
          Md:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          azm:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          takeoff:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          dist:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Pwt:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          Swt:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          pamp:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          codalenObs:
            type: number
            description: Todo description | ???
            format: double
          ccntr:
            type: array
            items:
              description: Todo description | ???
              example:
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
          caav:
            type: array
            items:
              description: Todo description | ???
              example:
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
                - 0
          amplitude:
            type: number
            description: Amplitude (Normally peak-to-peak) | col55 F7.2
            format: float
          ampUnitsCode:
            type: integer
            format: int64
            description: 'Amp units code. 0=PP mm, 1=0 to peak mm (UCB), 2=digital counts | col62 I2'
          ampType:
            type: integer
            format: int64
            description: Amplitude type 0=unspecified 1=Wood-Anderson 2=velocity 3=acceleration 4=no magnitude | col114 I2
          ampMag:
            type: number
            description: Amplitude magnitude for this station | col98 F3.2
            format: float
          ampMagWeightCode:
            type: integer
            format: int64
            description: Amplitude magnitude weight code | col82 I1
          importanceP:
            type: number
            description: Importance of P arrival | col101 F4.3
            format: float
          importanceS:
            type: number
            description: Importance of S arrival | col105 F4.3
            format: float
    magnitudeSchema:
      properties:
        ewMessage:
          required:
            - quakeId
            - version
            - mag
          properties:
            quakeId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id_localspace'
            version:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/type_origin__version_name'
            mag:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__mag'
            error:
              type: number
              description: Magnitude error | double
              format: double
              example: 0.52
            quality:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__quality'
            minDist:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__min_dist'
            azimuth:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/azimutal_gap'
            nStations:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__nsta'
            nChannels:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__ncha'
            qAuthor:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/qAuthor'
            qddsVersion:
              type: number
              description: qddsVersion description
              format: double
              example: 0
            iMagType:
              type: number
              description: iMagType description
              format: double
              example: 1
            magType:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/type_magnitude__name'
            algorithm:
              type: string
              description: algorithm description
              format: double
              example: MED
            ingvQuality:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/magnitude__mag_quality'
            phases:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/magnitude__phases'
        ewLogo:
          required:
            - type
            - module
            - installation
            - instance
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              description: Type description | ???
              example: TYPE_MAGNITUDE
            module:
              type: string
              description: Module description | ???
              example: MOD_LOCALMAG_PREL
            installation:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__installation'
            user:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__user'
            hostname:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__hostname'
            instance:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__instance'

    magnitude__phases:
      type: array
      items:
        required:
          - net
          - sta
          - comp
          - loc
          - time1
          - amp1
          - time2
          - amp2
        properties:
          net:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/net'
          sta:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/sta'
          comp:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/cha'
          loc:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/loc'
          mag:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/stationmagnitude__mag'
          dist:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/ep_distance_km'
          corr:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/stationmagnitude__mag_correction'
          time1:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__time1'
          amp1:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__amp1'
          period1:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__period'
          time2:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__time2'
          amp2:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__amp2'
          period2:
            $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/amplitude__period'
    pick_scnlSchema:
      properties:
        ewMessage:
          required:
            - pickId
          properties:
            pickId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id_localspace'
            network:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/net'
            station:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/sta'
            component:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/cha'
            location:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/loc'
            firstMotion:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/pick__firstmotion'
            pickWeight:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/pick__lower_uncertainty'
            timeOfPick:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/pick__arrival_time'
            pAmplitude:
              type: array
              items:
                type: number
                format: double
                description: peak P-wave half amplitude | ???
              example: [109, 101, 122]
        ewLogo:
          required:
            - type
            - module
            - installation
            - instance
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              description: Type description | ???
              example: TYPE_PICK_SCNL
            module:
              type: string
              description: Module description | ???
              example: MOD_PICK_EW
            installation:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__installation'
            user:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__user'
            hostname:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__hostname'
            instance:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__instance'
      
    strongmotioniiSchema:
      properties:
        ewMessage:
          required:
            - quakeId
            - version
          properties:
            quakeId:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/id_localspace'        
            version:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/type_origin__name'
            network:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/net'
            station:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/sta'
            component:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/cha'
            location:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/loc'
            qAuthor:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/qAuthor'            
            time:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__t_dt'
            alternateTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion_alt__t_alt_dt'
            alternateCode:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion_alt__altcode'
            pga:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__pga'
            pgaTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__tpga_dt'
            pgv:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__pgv'
            pgvTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__tpgv_dt'
            pgd:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__pgd'
            pgdTime:
              $ref: 'https://ingv.github.io/openapi/definitions.yaml#/components/schemas/strongmotion__tpgd_dt'
            RSA:
              type: array
              items:
                properties:
                  value:
                    type: number
                    format: double
                    description: RSA(response spectrum accel) value for period
                    example: 0.000724
                  period:
                    type: number
                    format: double
                    description: Period
                    example: 0.3 
        ewLogo:
          required:
            - type
            - module
            - installation
            - instance
          properties:
            type:
              type: string
              description: Type description | ???
              example: TYPE_STRONGMOTIONII
            module:
              type: string
              description: Module description | ???
              example: MOD_GMEW
            installation:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__installation'
            user:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__user'
            hostname:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__hostname'
            instance:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ewLogo__instance'
